@startuml RecruiterVerificationSequence
title 1.2.2 Recruiter Verification Flow - Sequence Diagram

actor "Recruiter" as R
participant "System" as S
actor "Moderator" as M

R -> S: Step 1: Register recruiter account
activate S
S --> R: Account created, email verification sent
deactivate S

R -> S: Step 2: Complete company profile (fields, documents)
activate S
S -> S: Step 3: Calculate profile completeness (%)

alt Profile < 97%
  S --> R: Step 4 (If profile < 97%): List of missing fields
  R -> S: Update profile fields
  S -> S: Step 3: Recalculate completeness (loop)
end

S -> S: Profile >= 97% -> Create verification request\n(status = PENDING)
S -> M: Send verification request

M -> S: Step 5: Open verification request
activate M

alt Approve
  M -> S: Step 6 (If approved): Approve + issue verified badge
  S -> S: company.status = VERIFIED
else Reject
  M -> S: Step 6 (If rejected): Reject with reason
  S -> S: company.status = REJECTED
end

S --> R: Step 7: Notify verification result
deactivate M

note over R, S
  BR-RV-05: Rejected profile can be updated
  and resubmitted -> loop back to Step 2
end note

@enduml
